a:entry.reducedTitle: Xbox September Weekender - Ibiza Rocks Hotel
a:entry.reducedDescription: Following in the footsteps of the massive Ibiza Rocks Hotel launch party, and the legendary Radio 1 Weekender, the final Xbox Weekender provided an epic climax to an amazing summer. The line-up didn’t disappoint with Mystery Jets, The Cuban Brothers and Zane Lowe putting in great performances where the likes of The Whip, Esser, Pilooski, Clik Clik, Ok Tokyo and Filthy Dukes had already been back in July and August. Not to mention mind blowing Rock Band performances from the Rock Band Live final…
a:entry.fullTitle: Xbox September Weekender - Ibiza Rocks Hotel
a:entry.fullDescription: Following in the footsteps of the massive Ibiza Rocks Hotel launch party, and the legendary Radio 1 Weekender, the final Xbox Weekender provided an epic climax to an amazing summer. The line-up didn’t disappoint with Mystery Jets, The Cuban Brothers and Zane Lowe putting in great performances where the likes of The Whip, Esser, Pilooski, Clik Clik, Ok Tokyo and Filthy Dukes had already been back in July and August. Not to mention mind blowing Rock Band performances from the Rock Band Live finalists.
